00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.492
Abortion until week 14,

00:00:02.690 --> 00:00:03.809
although it is possible

00:00:04.267 --> 00:00:07.489
week 22 if there is a risk to the mother

00:00:07.587 --> 00:00:09.752
or the fetus has an anomaly.

00:00:09.827 --> 00:00:11.036
Is Spain free?

00:00:11.037 --> 00:00:11.967
Yes, it's free,

00:00:11.968 --> 00:00:12.979
but normally

00:00:12.980 --> 00:00:15.227
you're going to find a lot of Cola in social security

00:00:15.228 --> 00:00:16.213
and most of

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.560
produce in private clinics.

00:00:18.561 --> 00:00:22.131
The cost of this will be between 300 to â‚¬600.

00:00:22.189 --> 00:00:23.798
There are certain provinces in Spain

00:00:23.799 --> 00:00:24.241
in which

00:00:24.242 --> 00:00:26.888
there is no Voluntary Termination of Pregnancy Center,

00:00:26.889 --> 00:00:27.988
but probably

00:00:27.989 --> 00:00:30.101
in the neighboring provinces there are,

00:00:30.102 --> 00:00:32.089
so you can travel by bus

00:00:32.090 --> 00:00:34.486
or by train to get to your Center.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:35.635
If you are of legal age

00:00:35.636 --> 00:00:37.211
you won't have any kind of problem,

00:00:37.212 --> 00:00:40.001
but if you are between the ages of 16 and 18,

00:00:40.002 --> 00:00:42.098
so you will need permission from your parents.

00:00:42.535 --> 00:00:44.153
and if you want to terminate 1 pregnancy, 

00:00:44.153 --> 00:00:44.770
how do we do it?

00:00:44.771 --> 00:00:45.632
First things first

00:00:45.633 --> 00:00:46.732
is to request 1 appointment

00:00:46.733 --> 00:00:49.562
in your Voluntary Pregnancy Intervention Center

00:00:49.563 --> 00:00:50.971
of your autonomous community

00:00:50.972 --> 00:00:51.771
or your province.

00:00:52.280 --> 00:00:53.725
How do you find these centers? 

00:00:53.725 --> 00:00:54.192
Very easy,

00:00:54.193 --> 00:00:55.709
you can ask your doctor,

00:00:55.711 --> 00:00:58.128
you can go to 1 Family Planning Center

00:00:58.291 --> 00:00:59.982
or in the association of clinics

00:00:59.983 --> 00:01:02.289
accredited for termination of pregnancy

00:01:02.291 --> 00:01:04.674
who have 1 list of all the centers in Spain.

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.100
When you arrive at the Center,

00:01:06.101 --> 00:01:07.221
in the same act

00:01:07.222 --> 00:01:09.761
all steps will be solved

00:01:09.762 --> 00:01:10.621
to be followed.

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:11.860
In 1 closed envelope

00:01:11.861 --> 00:01:14.501
will give you all the information about help

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:15.600
and after that

00:01:15.601 --> 00:01:17.371
you will have to wait at least 3 days

00:01:17.372 --> 00:01:19.437
in order to submit you to the voucher.

00:01:19.438 --> 00:01:20.213
When the day comes, 

00:01:20.213 --> 00:01:21.453
what will the procedure be like?

00:01:21.454 --> 00:01:23.473
First you have to come on an empty stomach,

00:01:23.474 --> 00:01:24.853
you have to go with your ID card

00:01:24.854 --> 00:01:26.381
with 1 previous ultrasound

00:01:26.382 --> 00:01:28.251
and with 1 previous blood test.

00:01:28.252 --> 00:01:29.801
Also when you arrive

00:01:29.859 --> 00:01:32.334
you will be given some papers to fill in,

00:01:32.335 --> 00:01:33.555
will do another ultrasound

00:01:33.556 --> 00:01:35.275
to confirm the week of pregnancy

00:01:35.276 --> 00:01:36.661
and see how the uterus is

00:01:36.739 --> 00:01:39.570
and another new blood test will also be made for you.

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:40.866
In case you are nervous.

00:01:40.867 --> 00:01:42.931
You will also be given psychological support

00:01:43.009 --> 00:01:44.323
for you to do what you do

00:01:44.324 --> 00:01:45.838
do it because you choose it

00:01:45.839 --> 00:01:48.131
and not because you have pressure or feel guilty.

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:49.020
After this

00:01:49.021 --> 00:01:51.142
will be switched to termination of pregnancy,

00:01:51.143 --> 00:01:54.501
either surgically orly

00:01:54.502 --> 00:01:56.897
and after 1 time of supervision you will be discharged.

00:01:56.967 --> 00:01:57.613
In Spain, 

00:01:57.613 --> 00:01:59.100
fortunately it is free,

00:01:59.101 --> 00:02:01.063
is free and secure

00:02:01.194 --> 00:02:03.545
and no one is forcing you to do something you don't want to do.

00:02:03.834 --> 00:02:05.282
So USE your rights

00:02:05.554 --> 00:02:07.565
and if at any time you want to be a Mother, 

00:02:07.565 --> 00:02:07.840
be it,

00:02:07.841 --> 00:02:09.263
but it doesn't have to be now
